Clean,Power,Research,features,SolarAnywhere,an,API,created,with,the,aim,to,produce,robust,applications,using,analytics,This,RESTful,API,allows,access,to,data,related,to,direct,normal,irradiance,global,horizontal,irradiance,and,horizontal,irradiance,at,regular,time,It,can,also,display,yearly,and,monthly,information,with,the,goal,to,present,multiple,spatial,and,temporal,resolutions,One,of,the,simulation,alternatives,includes,a,list,of,energy,calculation,with,a,solar,obstruction,space,angle,The,energy,systems,are,recognized,by,location,using,latitude,longitude,or,ZIP,code,Data,related,to,irradiance,wind,and,temperature,will,be,displayed,either,in,XML,or,CSV,formats